description: Try our easy to follow Eggplant Relish recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Relish,Pescatarian,Eggplant,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Gluten free,Egg free,Low sugar,Mother's Day,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Vegan,Tomato,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Eggplant Relish Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat olive oil in a saucepan. Add red onion and eggplant. Cook, stirring, for 10 minutes or until soft.
Add korma curry paste. Stir until combined and aromatic.
Add diced tomatoes, apple cider vinegar and 1/2 cup water. Stir until mixture comes to the boil. Simmer, partly covered, for 30 minutes or until very soft. Serve.
